{"id":478195432,"lang":"java","time":"1 year, 3 months","timestamp":1617903513,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"5 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/478195432/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"40.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int myAtoi(String s) {\n        if(s.length()==0)\n            return 0;\n        int index=0;\n        while(s.length()-1!=index && s.charAt(index)== 32)\n            index++;\n        int end=index;\n        if(s.charAt(index)=='+')\n        {\n            index++;\n            end++;\n        }\n        else if(s.charAt(end)=='-')\n            end++;\n        if(end==s.length() || s.charAt(end)<'0' || s.charAt(end)>'9')\n            return 0;\n        while(end!=s.length() && s.charAt(end)>=48 && s.charAt(end)<=57)\n            end++;\n        s=s.substring(index,end);\n        if(Double.parseDouble(s) >= 2147483647)\n            return 2147483647;\n        if(Double.parseDouble(s) <= -2147483648)\n            return -2147483648;\n        return Integer.parseInt(s);\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi"}
